      • getCategories

        public <any> getCategories()
        Description copied from interface: FeedManager
        Request categories list from cache. If none found, network request will be performed.

        If found in cache but expired - will return cached one and perform network request for updates.

        So, onNext may be called more than once!!!

        Specified by:
        getCategories in interface FeedManager
        Returns:
        Returns GfycatCategoriesList observable.

        Subscribe for Gfycat changes in local DB.

        !!! Important: You should NOT forget to unsubscribe, otherwise memory leak will occur.

        public Completable getNewGfycats(FeedDescription feedDescription)
        Description copied from interface: FeedManager
        Perform a network request of new Gfycats for a specified . FeedData containing this request result will be returned via FeedManager.observeGfycats(Context, FeedIdentifier) observable.

        NOTE: This works only with FeedDescription obtained via PublicFeedIdentifier.trending().

      • getMoreGfycats

        public Completable getMoreGfycats(FeedDescription feedDescription)
        Description copied from interface: FeedManager
        Perform a network request of more Gfycats for corresponding feed. Will download Gfycats and save to local DB if needed.

        FeedData containing this request result will be returned via FeedManager.observeGfycats(Context, FeedIdentifier) observable.
